name: PetroTal Corp.
longDescription: PetroTal Corp is an oil and gas company. The company is engaged in the exploration, appraisal, and development of crude oil and natural gas in Peru, South America. It generates revenues from the sale of crude oil. The company's operation includes Block 95 - Bretana oil field and Block 107 - Osheki Prospect.
